data.description: Looking to start or expand your portfolio of investment properties?  Look no further.  This side-by-side duplex has been meticulously maintained by the owner for many years.   2 beds/ 1 bath on each side.  Easy equity to be made by adding a bed and bath to each unit in the lower level.  New carpet in the bedrooms.  Updated appliances in the kitchens.   Freshly painted interior.  Separate gas/electric.  Private setting in the backyard.  Easy access to public transportation and the future light rail line.  This property is truly rent-ready.  Come take a look today!
